		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/11/rt-interview-recent-iran-nuclear-deal.html" title="Permalink to RT interview about the recent Iran nuclear deal" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">RT</span> interview about the recent Iran nuclear deal</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/11/rt-interview-recent-iran-nuclear-deal.html" title="11:41" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-11-26T11:41:21+00:00" pubdate>November 26, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
