	<article id="post-3428" class="post-3428 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-gchq category-intelligence category-isc category-law category-national-security category-nsa category-rttv category-snowden category-spies category-surveillance category-tv tag-accountability-2 tag-d-notice tag-edward-snowden tag-gchq tag-isc tag-nsa tag-oversight tag-rt">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/10/rt-interview-spy-oversight.html" title="Permalink to RT interview on spy oversight" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">RT</span> interview on spy oversight</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/10/rt-interview-spy-oversight.html" title="18:20" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-10-27T18:20:43+00:00" pubdate>October 27, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/10/rt-interview-spy-oversight.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here’s my <a href="http://rt.com/op-edge/global-spying-uk-media-792/">inter­view on <span class="caps">RT</span></a> about the fail­ure of polit­ical over­sight of the spies in the <span class="caps">UK</span> and <span class="caps">US</span>:<br />
<iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/77890046" height="281" width="500" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/77890046"><span class="caps">RT</span>: Snowden files reveal spy agency’s efforts to escape legal chal­lenge</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.<br />
Also pos­ted on <a href="http://www.maxkeiser.com/2013/10/gchquestions-snowden-files-reveal-spy-agencys-efforts-to-escape-leg/">www​.maxkeiser​.com</a>.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/10/rt-interview-spy-oversight.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
